---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---

<Section text="Education" href="education">
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="mb-1.5 font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
      CUNY Baruch College, Zicklin School of Business
    </h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start pb-5">
      <h4 class="mb-0.5 font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-primary">
        Master of Science in Business Analytics
      </h4>
      <span class="pb-[2px] text-sm text-white/70">2024</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="list-none">
      <li class="relative mb-3 pl-8 text-base text-neutral before:absolute before:top-1 before:left-0 before:content-[url(/check.svg)]">
        Focused on predictive modeling, data visualization, and big data technologies.
      </li>
      <li class="relative mb-3 pl-8 text-base text-neutral before:absolute before:top-1 before:left-0 before:content-[url(/check.svg)]">
        Completed projects in natural language processing, feature engineering, and dashboard design using Python and Power BI.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="mb-1.5 font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
      CUNY Queens College
    </h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start pb-5">
      <h4 class="mb-0.5 font-serif text-2xl font-medium text-primary">
        Bachelor of Arts in Sociology
      </h4>
      <span class="pb-[2px] text-sm text-white/70">2019</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="list-none">
      <li class="relative mb-3 pl-8 text-base text-neutral before:absolute before:top-1 before:left-0 before:content-[url(/check.svg)]">
        Built a foundation in social research methods, statistics, and behavioral analysis that complement data-driven decision-making.
      </li>
      <li class="relative mb-3 pl-8 text-base text-neutral before:absolute before:top-1 before:left-0 before:content-[url(/check.svg)]">
        Developed strong analytical writing and data interpretation skills through applied sociological projects.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Section>
